The goal is `↑n.factorial > e * (↑n / e) ^ n`
Our hypothesis `h1` is `n.factorial > (n / e) ^ n * e`

These are equivalent because multiplication is commutative and associative. We can use `nlinarith` or `linarith` to handle the rearrangement.

```tactics
