```

We need to show $(k+1) \cdot k! > e \cdot \left(\frac{k+1}{e}\right)^{k+1}$

```tactics
have h3 : (k : ℝ) / e > 0 := by positivity
```

We need to show $(k+1) \cdot k! > e \cdot \left(\frac{k+1}{e}\right)^{k+1}$

```tactics
